\f1 \cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Did you catch that\'85Elijah did amazing things, even though he wasn\'92t amazing.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}There was nothing special about him.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We want to always go to what people did and then assume what people do must be because of who people are\'85but what if we we\'92re all the same and all have the same potential, it just whether we dream and pray big enough for God?\
