\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Let me promise you that in 2016\'85we\'92re going to light the match!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}It is in us and I refuse to quench the spirit of God and what He wants for us any longer with weak small dreams.  \
